text: Ego ealdredusepiscopus cum licentia venerandae familiae inuuigornacivitate dabo viro nominebalwine.vico qui vocaturwesttun.

Familiae sancte mariae restituaturealdred. wulfward. berhtwald. mannig. harold. odda. raulf. æglwine. wulfwig. wilstan. wulfstan. edwig. ælfstan. þurkyll. godric. leofwine. wulfwig. godwine. berhtric. tosti. ælfstan. mannig. ælfnoð. leofwine. godwine. earkyll. eadmær. ealdred. ælfric. æglric. twegra hida geanboc & anre gerde æt westtune þe ealdred gebocade baldwine his stiwarde þreora manna dæg.
